&lt;h1 id="securitize-citizenship"&gt;Securitize Citizenship!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nov 29 2005&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;People hate immigration and immigrants as it&amp;rsquo;s seen as competing with newcomers over finite resources in a zero-sum game. This argument is flawed on many economic levels, but let&amp;rsquo;s overlook that for a moment. Let&amp;rsquo;s give everyone a stake.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>High Resolution Fundraising</title><link>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/hiresfund/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/hiresfund/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_zh/hiresfund/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
